---
import LegalLayout from '~/layouts/LegalLayout.astro';
import { BRAND_NAME, BRAND_LEGAL_NAME, CONTACT_EMAIL } from '~/data/site';
---

<LegalLayout routeKey="terms">
  <p>
    These Terms govern your use of fairledger.io and any associated tools or
    APIs operated by {BRAND_LEGAL_NAME}. By using the site you agree to them.
    If you do not agree, do not use the site.
  </p>

  <h2>1. Eligibility</h2>
  <p>
    You must be at least 18 years old (or 21 in jurisdictions where the local
    minimum gambling age is higher) to use {BRAND_NAME}. You confirm that
    accessing the site is legal where you live.
  </p>

  <h2>2. What we are not</h2>
  <p>
    {BRAND_NAME} is a publisher and a tool maker. We are <strong>not</strong> a
    casino, a sportsbook, a payment processor, a wallet or a financial advisor.
    Nothing on this site is gambling advice, financial advice, legal advice or
    a solicitation to gamble.
  </p>

  <h2>3. Affiliate links</h2>
  <p>
    Most outbound links to operators are affiliate links. When you sign up via
    one of these links the operator pays us a share of their net gaming revenue
    from your account. This relationship is disclosed on every link with the
    rel="sponsored" attribute and on our <a href="/disclaimer/">disclosure page</a>.
  </p>

  <h2>4. Wager-share program</h2>
  <p>
    Wager-share is a discretionary loyalty program. We pay between 50% and 100%
    of the affiliate revenue an operator pays us back to the user who generated
    it. Eligibility, payout schedule and excluded games are listed on the
    <a href="/leaderboard/">leaderboard</a> page. We may pause, suspend or
    terminate the program for fraud, abuse, multi-accounting or operator
    chargebacks.
  </p>

  <h2>5. User-submitted content</h2>
  <p>
    If you submit a casino dispute, a data correction or a comment, you grant
    {BRAND_NAME} a worldwide, non-exclusive, royalty-free licence to publish it
    in our editorial content. You confirm the submission is accurate and does
    not infringe a third party's rights.
  </p>

  <h2>6. Intellectual property</h2>
  <p>
    All site copy, logo, ranking algorithm and on-chain dataset are the property
    of {BRAND_LEGAL_NAME}. The wallet ledger and ranking-algorithm source code
    are released under the MIT licence on our public GitHub. Site copy is
    released under CC-BY-4.0 with attribution to {BRAND_NAME}.
  </p>

  <h2>7. Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
  <p>
    The site is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. While we work
    hard to keep our deposit-volume figures, bonus codes and review scores
    accurate, we do not warrant that any number on the site is current or
    error-free. Always verify with the operator before depositing.
  </p>

  <h2>8. Limitation of liability</h2>
  <p>
    To the maximum extent permitted by law, {BRAND_LEGAL_NAME} shall not be
    liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential or punitive
    damages arising from your use of the site, including any losses you incur
    by gambling at an operator we cover. Our total liability for any direct
    losses is limited to GBP 100.
  </p>

  <h2>9. Termination</h2>
  <p>
    We may suspend access to the site for any user found to be scraping at
    abusive rates, automating the wager-share dashboard or attempting to harm
    the service.
  </p>

  <h2>10. Governing law</h2>
  <p>
    These Terms are governed by the laws of England and Wales. Any dispute
    shall be resolved exclusively in the courts of England.
  </p>

  <h2>11. Contact</h2>
  <p>
    For any question about these Terms, email <a href={`mailto:${CONTACT_EMAIL}`}>{CONTACT_EMAIL}</a>.
  </p>
</LegalLayout>
